Class Connector

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.client.io.Connector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RMIConnector, SocketConnector
    public abstract class Connector
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.AutoCloseable
    This class represents the entity which manages the IO of messages between the client and the server
